  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The Animal Companion grows one size category, increasing its weight eightfold and granting it a +8 size bonus to Strength, a +4 size bonus to Constitution and a -2 size penalty to Dexterity. Its natural armor increases by 2, and it suffers the appropriate new bonuses/penalties according to its size. The companion also gains DR 5/Chakra and a +2 resistance bonus to saves. If there is not enough space for the companion to grow, it may make a Strength check (DC based on environment) to burst through any restraints (such as if it is tied up or in a very small area). If it fails, it stops growing.<br><br>Once the technique ends, the companion will be @Condition[fatigued]{fatigued} for the rest of the encounter. While fatigued, it cannot benefit from this technique again.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
